{
  "title": "Sauna Controller with Evaporator",
  "xml_type": "",
  "kb_slug": "sauna-controller-evaporator",
  "description": "Sauna controller with Evaporator\nUsing this Function Block, a Sauna with an Evaporator can be intelligently automated\nAll standard Sauna heaters can be controlled (switching of the heating elements, as well as analog control via 0-10 V signal).\nAn Evaporator can be switched On / Off, but also controlled via an analog 0-10 V signal.",
